reviewText: In my opinion the production of the rendezvous was very well done when it came to scenery etc. The topic, "competition" basically only cover knife and hawk throwing!! There is far more to a rendezvous than that. So I was very disappointed in having to watch that long of a video only covering that one event. I would not buy this video!!!!

In purchasing this video, I thought I was purchasing a video of a complete Rendezvous segment because of the price.  I was fooled.  Not much information for the elevated price that you pay.  My only review is that it is totally not worth the money.
